=Desarrollo=
----

==Aplicaciones Android==
<p class="pubdate">Fechas: <time>2012-09-15</time>

Juan has developed an Android application that allows you to monitorize the bluetooth communication, adjust some robot parameters and control the robot with joysticks. Only touching your mobile screen! :-D

There is still some work to do to allow manual-auto switching, to support other Android versions, etc.. Help us!

----

==Comunicación Bluetooth==
<p class="pubdate">Fechas: <time>2012-08-15</time>

We are using a very little and affordable (from $4 to $7) bluettoth communication device. We have already configured it and developed C code to make it work with the Maple Mini and parse the commands that your receive from the outside.

